<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">1.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;"> 解析权重文件结构，确定各层维度。</span></span>
